absolutely%20no%20tariff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20set%20to%20take%20effect%20April%202%20and%20impact%20foreign-made%20cars%20and%20light%20trucks%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20existing%20tariffs%20on%20those%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20returning%20to%20the%20presidency%20in%20January%2C%20Trump%20has%20already%20imposed%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20major%20US%20trading%20partners%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%20and%20China%20--%20as%20well%20as%20a%2025%20percent%20duty%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminum%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20previously%20offered%20automakers%20temporary%20reprieve%20from%20the%20levies%20affecting%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20over%20Trump's%20trade%20plans%20and%20worries%20they%20could%20trigger%20a%20downturn%20have%20roiled%20financial%20markets%2C%20with%20consumer%20confidence%20also%20falling%20in%20recent%20months%20amid%20fears%20of%20the%20tariffs'%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20slumped%20ahead%20of%20Trump's%20announcement%2C%20with%20the%20tech-focused%20Nasdaq%20plunging%202.0%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20in%20automaker%20General%20Motors%20closed%203.1%20percent%20down%2C%20while%20Ford%20eked%20out%20a%200.1%20percent%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20referred%20to%20levies%20as%20a%20way%20to%20raise%20government%20revenue%2C%20revitalize%20American%20industry%20and%20press%20countries%20on%20US%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20targeting%20imported%20cars%20could%20strain%20ties%20with%20countries%20like%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%20and%20Germany%20--%20which%20are%20close%20US%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2050%20percent%20of%20cars%20sold%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20manufactured%20within%20the%20country.%20Among%20imports%2C%20about%20half%20come%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20with%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%20and%20Germany%2C%20also%20major%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Center%20for%20Automotive%20Research%20has%20previously%20estimated%20that%20US%20tariffs%20%E2%80%93-%20including%20those%20on%20metals%20and%20imported%20autos%20%E2%80%93-%20could%20increase%20the%20price%20of%20a%20car%20by%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20and%20weigh%20on%20the%20jobs%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Liberation%20Day'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20automobile%20industry%2C%20Trump%20has%20also%20been%20eyeing%20sector-specific%20tariffs%20on%20industries%20like%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20semiconductors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20reaffirmed%20his%20intent%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20lumber%20and%20pharmaceuticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20announcement%20on%20autos%20comes%20ahead%20of%20April%202%2C%20which%20Trump%20has%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20promised%20reciprocal%20levies%20on%20the%20date%2C%20tailored%20to%20different%20trading%20partners%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20remedy%20practices%20that%20Washington%20deemed%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20if%20further%20sector-specific%20tariffs%20would%20be%20announced%20on%20April%202%2C%20with%20the%20White%20House%20noting%20this%20week%20that%20the%20situation%20remained%20fluid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20reporters%20Monday%20that%20he%20might%20%26quot%3Bgive%20a%20lot%20of%20countries%20breaks%26quot%3B%20eventually%2C%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Newsmax%20on%20Tuesday%3A%20%26quot%3BI'll%20probably%20be%20more%20lenient%20than%20reciprocal%2C%20because%20if%20I%20was%20reciprocal%2C%20that%20would%20be%20very%20tough%20for%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20added%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20too%20many%20exceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHopes%20of%20a%20narrower%20tariff%20rollout%20had%20given%20financial%20markets%20a%20boost%2C%20but%20investors%20remain%20jittery%20over%20rapid%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump%20has%20invoked%20emergency%20economic%20powers%20for%20some%20recent%20tariffs%2C%20his%20auto%20levies%20may%20build%20on%20a%20previous%20government%20investigation%20completed%20in%202019%2C%20former%20US%20trade%20official%20Ryan%20Majerus%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20found%20that%20excessive%20imports%20were%20weakening%20the%20internal%20economy%20and%20might%20impair%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20one%20recommendation%20was%20to%20institute%20tariffs%20of%20up%20to%2025%20percent%20to%20bolster%20US%20production%20of%20autos%20and%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20advantage%20with%20autos%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Majerus%2C%20now%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20King%20%26amp%3B%20Spalding%20law%20firm%2C%20is%20that%20the%20administration%20%26quot%3Bcan%20act%20a%20lot%20quicker%20if%20they%20want%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%2C%20say%20in%20lumber%20or%20copper%2C%20where%20they%20had%20to%20launch%20investigations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20trade%20partners%20have%20been%20furthering%20talks%20with%20Washington%20as%20Trump's%20reciprocal%20tariff%20deadline%20looms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20trade%20chief%20Maros%20Sefcovic%20met%20his%20American%20counterparts%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20and%20trade%20envoy%20Jamieson%20Greer%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESefcovic%20said%20on%20social%20media%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20EU's%20priority%20is%20a%20fair%2C%20balanced%20deal%20instead%20of%20unjustified%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743027720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fod7s9lk8_donald-trump-reuters_625x3