0black%20was%20what%20she%20had%20absorbed%20--%20so%20much%20so%20that%20as%20a%20four-year-old%2C%20she%20had%20asked%20her%20mother%20to%20put%20her%20back%20in%20the%20womb%20and%20%26quot%3Bbring%20me%20out%20again%2C%20all%20white%20and%20pretty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20perception%20changed%20only%20when%20she%20saw%20herself%20with%20the%20eyes%20of%20her%20grown%20up%20children.%20Today%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20dig%20black%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBlack%20is%20the%20all-pervasive%20truth%20of%20the%20universe.%20Black%20is%20that%20which%20can%20absorb%20anything%2C%20the%20most%20powerful%20pulse%20of%20energy%20known%20to%20humankind.%20It%20is%20the%20colour%20that%20works%20on%20everyone%2C%20the%20dress%20code%20for%20office%2C%20the%20lustre%20of%20evening%20wear%2C%20the%20essence%20of%20kajol%2C%20the%20promise%20of%20rain%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743011040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fvlhm9avg_kerala-bureaucrat-sarada-muraleedharan_625x300_26_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftime-we-re-wrote-what-black-means-kerala-chief-secretary-sarada-muraleedharan-to-ndtv-8018596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20Chief%20Secretary%20Sarada%20Muraleedharan%2C%20who%20triggered%20a%20huge%20conversation%20online%20about%20colorism%20after%20facing%20the%20brunt%20of%20it%2C%20told%20NDTV%20today%20that%20she%20had%20deleted%20her%20post%20and%20then%20restored%20it%20after%20being%20asked%20to%20by%20a%20number%20of%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202025%3A%20Quinton%20De%20Kock's%2097%20Guides%20KKR%20To%20Easy%208-Wicket%20Win%20Over%20RR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajasthan%20Royals%20vs%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20Highlights%2C%20IPL%202025%3A%3C%2Fstro