Subramainam%2C%20a%20Europe-based%20Indian%20journalist%2C%20to%20expose%20the%20bribery%20scandal%20in%201987-89%2C%20has%20resurfaced.%20Italian%20business%20executive%20Ottavio%20Quattrocchi%20is%20back%20in%20the%20news.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0Three%20weeks%20after%20Subramaniam's%20book%2C%20Boforsgate%3A%20A%20Journalist's%20Pursuit%20Of%20Truth%2C%20hit%20the%20stands%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20has%20now%20demanded%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20resignations%20as%20Members%20of%20Parliament.%20The%20allegations%20are%20old%20and%20have%20been%20oft-repeated%20(in%20his%20order%20related%20to%20Bofors%20on%20November%2014%2C%202022%2C%20Special%20Judge%20Prem%20Kumar%20had%20detailed%20how%20since%201974%2C%20the%20Quattrocchis%20had%20regularly%20interacted%20with%20the%20Gandhis%20over%20%E2%80%98Italian%20food'%20and%20how%20their%20children%20grew%20up%20together).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20seems%20to%20be%20renewed%20interest%20in%20the%20Bofors%20case%2C%20which%20lingered%20in%20courts%20for%2025%20years%20before%20in%202011%2C%20a%20judge%20in%20Delhi's%20Tis%20Hazari%20courts%20discharged%20Quattrocchi%20from%20the%20payoffs%20case%20after%20allowing%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20withdraw%20prosecution%20against%20him%20(while%20the%20CBI%20didn't%20make%20any%20headway%2C%20an%20Income%20Tax%20Tribunal%20had%20established%20that%20Rs%2041%20lakh%20had%20been%20paid%20in%20bribes%20to%20Quattrocchi).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELetter%20Rogatory%20Sent%20To%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20last%20month%20made%20a%20judicial%20request%20to%20the%20United%20States%20after%20sending%20a%20%E2%80%98Letter%20Rogatory'%20(LR)%E2%80%94a%20written%20request%20sent%20by%20the%20court%20of%20one%20country%20to%20the%20that%20of%20another%20country%20to%20obtain%20assistance%20in%20the%20investigation%20or%20prosecution%20of%20a%20criminal%20matter%E2%80%94requesting%20information%20from%20private%20investigator%20Michael%20Hershman%20of%20an%20agency%20called%20Fairfax.%20Hershman%20had%20expressed%20willingness%20to%20share%20with%20Indian%20agencies%20crucial%20details%20about%20the%20%C2%A0Bofors%20bribery%20scandal%20way%20back%20in%201988.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20the%20process%20to%20send%20the%20LR%20was%20initiated%20on%20October%2014%2C%202024%2C%20and%20it%20was%20sent%20in%20February%20after%20approval%20from%20the%20court%20concerned.%20The%20CBI%20has%20also%20informed%20the%20special%20court%20hearing%20the%20agency's%20plea%20for%20further%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20bribery%20case%20about%20the%20recent%20developments.%20So%2C%20%E2%80%98Q'%20may%20soon%20be%20back%20in%20the%20limelight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmergence%20of%20%E2%80%98Q'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOttavio%20Quattrocchi%20had%20come%20to%20India%20as%20a%20representative%20of%20Italian%20petroleum%20company%20Eni%20and%20engineering%20giant%20Snamprogetti%2C%20both%20firms%20of%20repute%2C%20in%20the%20mid-1960s.%20His%20name%20surfaced%20in%20Parliament%20in%201981-82%20after%20Haldor%20Topsoe%2C%20a%20firm%20acquired%20by%20Snamprogetti%2C%20in%20September%201980%20bagged%20the%20prestigious%20contract%20for%20consultancy%20for%20setting%20up%20the%20world's%20largest%20gas-based%20urea%20plant%20in%20Thal%20Vaishet%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Mumbai.%20The%20project%2C%20set%20up%20under%20public%20sector%20company%20Rashtriya%20Chemicals%20%26amp%3B%20Fertilisers%20(RCF)%2C%20had%20been%20under%20consideration%20since%201976.%20The%20contractor%20chosen%20for%20Thal%20Vaishet%20was%20to%20be%20a%20frontrunner%20for%20a%20dozen%20more%20Bombay%20High%20gas-based%20fertilizer%20plants%20that%20came%20up%20in%20later%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20American%20Firm%2C%20CF%20Braun%2C%20had%20been%20shortlisted%20by%20a%20Committee%20of%20Secretaries%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%94the%20change%20of%20regime%20in%201977%20necessitated%20a%20review%20and%20CF%20Braun%20continued%20to%20head%20the%20list%20in%20the%20Janata%20regime%20as%20well.%20The%20ouster%20of%20Morarji%20Desai%20%C2%A0in%201979%20saw%20yet%20another%20review%20by%20H.N.%20Bahuguna%2C%20the%20Petroleum%20Minister%20of%20Charan%20Singh%20regime.%20The%20choice%20of%20CF%20Braun%20persisted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%201980%2C%20when%20Indira%20Gandhi%20returned%20to%20power%2C%20a%20review%20panel%20was%20set%20up%20yet%20again%20and%20CF%20Braun%2C%20represented%20in%20India%20by%20a%20firm%20headed%20by%20Narendra%20N.%20Kapadia%20(better%20known%20as%20Mama%20Kapadia)%2C%20a%20former%20Sheriff%20of%20Bombay%20and%20his%20nephew%2C%20Nanak%20Sheth%2C%20continued%20to%20be%20the%20prime%20choice%20initially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Gandhi%20died%20in%20June%201980.%20Power%20equations%20in%20New%20Delhi%20changed%20swiftly.%20In%20September%201980%2C%20the%20contract%20was%20awarded%20to%20Haldor%20Topsoe%2C%20a%20Snamprogetti%20affiliate%2C%20which%20had%20not%20figured%20in%20the%20deliberations%20of%20any%20of%20the%20panels%20hitherto.%20Quattrocchi's%20proximity%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Powers%20that%20Be'%20started%20buzzing%20in%20Lutyens'%20Delhi's%20grapevine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Q'%20Surfaces%20In%20Parliament%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20(S)%20stalwart%20K.P.%20Unnikrishnan%20(who%20later%20was%20Cabinet%20Minister%20under%20Vishwanath%20Pratap%20Singh)%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20award%20of%20contract%20for%20RCF%20Thal%20Vaishet%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20placed%20on%20the%20table%20of%20the%20House%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20deal%20file%20(authenticated%20by%20him%2C%20as%20per%20Lok%20Sabha%20rules%20in%20vogue%20since%20similar%20disclosures%20by%20Feroze%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20Mundhra%20scandal).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20Ottavio%20Quattrocchi%20surfaced%20in%20India's%20political%20discourse%2C%20thus.%20Though%20his%20proximity%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20talk%20of%20the%20town%2C%20it%20did%20not%20crop%20up%20during%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20such%20parliamentary%20disclosures%20in%20the%20past%20had%20resulted%20in%20furore%2C%20putting%20the%20government%20on%20the%20back%20foot.%20Feroze%20Gandhi's%20expos%C3%A9%20had%20resulted%20in%20the%20resignation%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20Finance%20Minister%20T.T.%20Krishnamachari.%20The%20government%20of%20Nehru's%20daughter%20chose%20not%20to%20play%20on%20the%20backfoot.%20It%20reacted%20by%20asking%20the%20CBI%20to%20probe%20the%20leakage%20of%20the%20government%20file%20cited%20by%20Unnikrishnan.%20An%20Official%20Secrets%20Act%20case%20was%20initiated.%20Mama%20Kapadia%20and%20Nanak%20Sheth%20were%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20the%20Thal%20Vishet%20deal%2C%20a%20new%20phase%20began%20not%20only%20in%20the%20petro-chemical%20industry%20with%20Snamprogetti%20snapping%20up%20one%20contract%20after%20another%2C%20but%20even%20in%20Parliamentary%20politics.%20Disclosure%20based%20on%20clinching%20evidence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20photocopies%20of%20official%20files%20also%20became%20a%20thing%20of%20yore.%20Innuendo%20or%20citing%20%E2%80%98disclosures%20from%20abroad'%20became%20the%20norm%20for%20raising%20allegations%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Extra-Technical%20Considerations'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Estimates%20Committee%20of%20the%207th%20Lok%20Sabha%20took%20note%20of%20the%20matter%20as%20the%20dilly-dallying%20in%20decision-making%20had%20caused%20a%20cost%20overrun.%20The%20reports%20of%20the%20Estimates%20Committee%20and%20of%20the%20Committee%20on%20Public%20Undertakings%2C%20which%20looked%20into%20Thal%20Vaishet%2C%20were%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20April%2016%2C%201982%20(21st%20report%20of%20the%20panel).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20panels%20noted%20that%20the%20then%20secretary%20of%20the%20concerned%20ministry%2C%20K.V.%20Ramanathan%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20the%20last-minute%20change%20in%20the%20choice%20of%20consultant%20for%20Thal%20Vaishet%20had%20been%20necessitated%20by%20%E2%80%98superior%20technical%20advice'%2C%20had%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20Sir%2C%20the%20change%20was%20necessitated%20by%20what%20I%20may%20term%20as%20superior%20extra-technical%20considerations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamanathan%20was%20senior-most%20in%20line%20of%20succession%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Cabinet%20Secretary.%20He%20was%20superseded%20(the%20first%20such%20supersession%20at%20apex%20level%20of%20bureaucracy)%20and%20accommodated%20in%20Planning%20Commission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamily%20Guests%20Of%20Quattrocchi's%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%201980%2C%20the%20Maino%20family%20from%20Italy%20visited%20India%20for%20Christmas.%20Perhaps%20it%20was%20thought%20that%20putting%20up%20foreign%20nationals%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20House%20wouldn't%20be%20prudent%2C%20thus%20the%20guests%20stayed%20in%20the%20Quattrocchi%20home%20in%20Friends%20Colony.%20Moreover%2C%20as%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20had%20died%20merely%20six%20months%20earlier%2C%20Christmas%20was%20not%20celebrated%20at%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOttavio%20and%20Maria%20Quattrocchi%20were%20regular%20invitees%20to%20Sunday%20brunches%20hosted%20by%20Rajiv%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20lawns%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20House.%20Their%20son%2C%20Massimo%2C%20worked%20in%20Bengaluru%20as%20a%20representative%20of%20a%20Luxembourg%20firm%20in%20the%20first%20part%20of%20the%20UPA%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMassimo%20Quattrocchi's%20trip%20to%20New%20Delhi%20in%202006%20and%20his%20%E2%80%98accidental'%20meeting%20at%20a%20party%20hosted%20by%20an%20MP%20with%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20while%20his%20father's%20extradition%20was%20being%20sought%20in%20Argentine%20by%20the%20CBI%2C%20had%20caused%20a%20buzz%20in%20Lutyens'%20grapevine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArrested%20due%20to%20Interpol's%20Red%20Corner%20notice%20on%20Bofors%2C%20Quattrocchi%20was%20let%20off%20by%20a%20court%20in%20Argentina.%20The%20judge%20recorded%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20did%20not%20present%20proper%20legal%20documents%E2%80%9D%20and%20put%20the%20burden%20of%20paying%20Quattrocchi's%20legal%20expenses%20on%20the%20Indian%20Embassy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Q'%20is%20back%20in%20the%20news%20today.%20Will%20the%20LR%20sent%20to%20the%20US%20yield%20new%20information%3F%20Or%20will%20%E2%80%98shoot%20and%20scoot'%2C%20a%20competency%20of%20the%20Bofors%20howitzer%20that%20helped%20India%20oust%20Pakistan%20from%20Kargil%20heights%20in%201999%2C%20remain%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20L'affaire%20Bofors%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPS%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQuattrocchi%20passed%20away%20in%20Milan%2C%20Italy%2C%20in%20July%202013.%20He%20had%20slipped%20away%20from%20India%20quietly%2C%20taking%20a%20midnight%20flight%2C%20soon%20after%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20in%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742995080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5km48hno_bofors_625x300_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmuch-before-bofors-this-deal-brought-q-into-limelight-8016628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ghost%20of%20'Q'%20from%20the%20Bofors%20scandal%20is%20back%20in%20the%20news%20today.%20Will%20the%20LR%20sent%20to%20the%20US%20yield%20new%20information%3F%20Or%20will%20'shoot%20and%20scoot'%20remain%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20Laffaire%20Bofors%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmuch-before-bofors-this-deal-brought-q-into-limelight-8016628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEntity%20Of%20Concern%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Shreds%20US%20Religious%20Freedom%20Body%20Over%20RAW%20Demand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strongly-worded%20rebuttal%2C%20India%20said%20today%20that%20it%20is%20the%20US%20religious%20freedom%20body%20USCIRF%20that%20should%20be%20designated%20internationally%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bentity%20of%20concern%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20repeated%20%26quot%3Bpattern%20of%20biased%20and%20politically%20motivated%20assessments%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisrepresentation%26quot%3B%20of%20facts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi's%20statement%20came%20hours%20after%20the%20US%20body's%20annual%20religious%20freedom%20report%20claimed%20that%20minorities%20in%20India%20continue%20to%20face%20deteriorating%20treatment.%20The%20panel's%20report%20also%20called%20for%20imposing%20sanctions%20on%20India's%20external%20intelligence%20agency%20R%26amp%3BAW%20over%20its%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bassassination%26quot%3B%20plots%20against%20'Khalistani'%20separatists%20and%20extremists%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20the%20recently%20released%202025%20Annual%20Report%20of%20the%20US%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20(USCIRF)%2C%20which%20once%20again%20continues%20its%20pattern%20of%20issuing%20biased%20and%20politically%20motivated%20assessments%2C%26quot%3B%20India's%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%2C%20raising%20concerns%20on%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20body%20over%20such%20%26quot%3Bagenda-based%26quot%3B%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndirectly%20calling%20the%20panel's%20report%20fake%2C%20India%20questioned%20if%20at%20all%20the%20USCIRF%20is%20even%20genuine%20in%20its%20work%20and%20concerns%20on%20religious%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20USCIRF's%20persistent%20attempts%20to%20misrepresent%20isolated%20incidents%20and%20cast%20aspersions%20on%20India's%20vibrant%20multicultural%20society%20reflect%20a%20deliberate%20agenda%20rather%20than%20a%20genuine%20concern%20for%20religious%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20the%20US%20religious%20freedom%20body%20is%20far%20from%20reality%2C%20New%20Delhi%20said%20it%20does%20not%20even%20expect%20the%20panel%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20truth.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20home%20to%201.4%20billion%20people%20who%20are%20adherents%20to%20all%20religions%20known%20to%20mankind.%20However%2C%20we%20have%20no%20expectation%20that%20the%20USCIRF%20will%20engage%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20India's%20pluralistic%20framework%20or%20acknowledge%20the%20harmonious%20coexistence%20of%20its%20diverse%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabeling%20the%20US%20religious%20freedom%20body%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20entity%20of%20concern%26quot%3B%2C%20India%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20efforts%20to%20undermine%20India's%20standing%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20democracy%20and%20tolerance%20will%20not%20succeed.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20USCIRF%20that%20should%20be%20designated%20as%20an%20entity%20of%20concern.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20US%20panel's%20recommendation%2C%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%20the%20US%20government%20will%20sanction%20India's%20external%20intelligence%20agency%20R%26amp%3BAW%20or%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Analysis%20Wing%20for%20its%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20plotting%20the%20killings%20of%20extremists%20and%20terrorists%20overseas.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20panel's%20views%20and%20recommendations%20are%20not%20binding%20on%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20current%20report%2C%20the%20US%20panel%20has%20recommended%20that%20India%20be%20designated%20as%20a%20%