3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742992200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fabcf-5-1707226745-1742987705.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D415619%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Himachal%20to%20Kerala%2C%20discover%20eco-friendly%20mud%20homestays%20across%20India%20that%20offer%20natural%20cooling%2C%20local%20charm%2C%20and%20a%20peaceful%20escape%20from%20the%20summer%20heat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Samreen%20Syed%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F415619%2Fbest-mud-homestays-india-summer-eco-travel%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Likely%20To%20Add%20150%20Million%20Room%20ACs%20By%202035%20Amid%20Peak%20Power%20Demand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20expected%20to%20add%20130-150%20million%20new%20room%20air%20conditioners%20(ACs)%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20which%20could%20increase%20the%20country's%20peak%20power%20demand%20by%20more%20than%20180%20gigawatts%20(GW)%20by%202035%2C%20straining%20the%20power%20system%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study%20published%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20by%20the%20India%20Energy%20and%20Climate%20Center%20(IECC)%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%20(UC)%20in%20Berkeley%20said%20the%20fastest-developing%20major%20economy%20can%20avoid%20severe%20power%20shortages%20and%20save%20consumers%20up%20to%20Rs%202.2%20lakh%20crore%20(USD%2026%20billion)%20by%20doubling%20the%20energy%20efficiency%20of%20room%20ACs%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20adds%2010-15%20million%20new%20ACs%20annually%2C%20with%20another%20130-150%20million%20expected%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20Without%20policy%20intervention%2C%20ACs%20alone%20could%20drive%20120%20GW%20of%20peak%20power%20demand%20by%202030%20and%20180%20GW%20by%202035%2C%20nearly%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20projected%20totals%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20growth%20is%20outpacing%20India's%20power%20supply%20and%20could%20lead%20to%20serious%20electricity%20shortages%20as%20early%20as%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nikit%20Abhyankar%2C%20the%20study's%20lead%20author%20and%20UC%20Berkeley%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BACs%20are%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20drivers%20of%20peak%20demand%2C%20and%20without%20intervention%2C%20we%20risk%20blackouts%20or%20costly%20emergency%20fixes.%20But%20with%20smart%20policy%2C%20we%20can%20turn%20this%20into%20a%20win%20for%20consumers%2C%20manufacturers%20and%20the%20grid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20reported%20on%20Monday%20that%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20experience%20a%20nine%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20growth%20in%20peak%20electricity%20demand%20this%20summer%20with%20the%20country%20expected%20to%20experience%20more%20heat%20waves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20all-India%20peak%20electricity%20demand%20crossed%20250%20GW%20on%20May%2030%2C%20which%20was%206.3%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%20projections.%20Climate%20change-induced%20heat%20stress%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20factors%20driving%20electricity%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20the%20household%20sector%20in%20India's%20total%20electricity%20consumption%20increased%20from%2022%20per%20cent%20in%202012-13%20to%2025%20per%20cent%20in%202022-23.%20Much%20of%20this%20rise%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20economic%20growth%20and%20the%20increasing%20need%20for%20cooling%20due%20to%20rising%20temperatures%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20room%20air%20conditioner%20sales%20surged%20by%2040%20to%2050%20per%20cent%20year-on-year%20amid%20record-breaking%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20ongoing%20research%20at%20the%20Oxford%20India%20Centre%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%2C%20the%20largest%20cooling%20demand%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20will%20come%20from%20India%2C%20followed%20by%20China%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Brazil%2C%20the%20Philippines%20and%20the%20US%20in%20a%20world%20two%20degrees%20Celsius%20warmer%20than%20pre-industrial%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20by%20the%20University%20of%20California%20recommends%20updating%20India's%20Minimum%20Energy%20Performance%20Standards%20(MEPS)%2C%20beginning%20with%20a%202027%20revision%20that%20raises%20the%201-star%20label%20to%20ISEER%205.0%20--%20equivalent%20to%20today's%205-star%20level%20--%20and%20tightening%20standards%20every%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20alone%20could%20avoid%2010%20GW%20of%20shortages%20by%202028%2C%2023%20GW%20by%202030%20and%2060%20GW%20by%202035%2C%20equivalent%20to%20120%20large%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20about%20long-term%20energy%20savings%3B%20it's%20an%20immediate%20grid%20reliability%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhyankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfficient%20ACs%20also%20offer%20massive%20consumer%20benefits.%20Even%20with%20slightly%20higher%20upfront%20prices%2C%20they%20could%20deliver%20net%20savings%20of%20Rs%2066%2C000%20to%20Rs%202%2C25%2C000%20crore%20(USD%208-26%20billion)%20by%202035%2C%20paying%20for%20themselves%20within%20two%20to%20three%20years%20through%20lower%20electricity%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20common%20concern%20with%20efficient%20ACs%20is%20that%20they%20might%20be%20more%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amol%20Phadke%2C%20co-author%20and%20UC%20Berkeley%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20our%20analysis%20of%20global%20markets%2C%20including%20India%2C%20shows%20that%20efficiency%20is%20not%20the%20main%20factor%20driving%20retail%20prices.%20With%20the%20right%20policy%20support%2C%20higher%20efficiency%20often%20goes%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20lower%20costs%2C%20thanks%20to%20economies%20of%20scale%2C%20better%20supply%20chains%20and%20competitive%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20600%20AC%20models%20--%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20offerings%20--%20already%20exceed%20India's%20top%20efficiency%20threshold%2C%20the%205-star%20level%2C%20with%20many%20produced%20by%20domestic%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20chance%20for%20Indian%20manufacturers%20to%20lead%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jose%20Dominguez%2C%20co-author%20and%20IECC%20researcher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20right%20policy%20signal%2C%20they%20can%20scale%20under%20Make%20in%20India%20and%20PLI%20(Production%20Linked%20Incentive)%20schemes%2C%20positioning%20India%20as%20a%20global%20hub%20for%20sustainable%20and%20affordable%20cooling%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20calls%20for%20updating%20AC%20test%20procedures%20to%20better%20reflect%20India's%20humid%20climate%2C%20where%20comfort%20depends%20not%20just%20on%20cooling%20but%20on%20moisture%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742991780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Faudp3n18_ac-generic-_625x300_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-likely-to-add-150-million-room-acs-by-2035-amid-peak-power-demand-8016119%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20expected%20to%20add%20130-150%20million%20new%20room%20air%20conditioners%20(ACs)%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20which%20could%20increase%20the%20country's%20peak%20power%20demand%20by%20more%20than%20180%20gigawatts%20by%202035%2C%20straining%20the%20power%20system%2C%20according%20to%20new%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%