tterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.48-1-1_11zon-1742741650-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.48-1-1_11zon-1742741650.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-415460%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESpice%20Up%20Foods%20makes%20lives%20easier%20for%20people%20who%20keep%20travelling%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20ready-to-eat%20healthy%20meals%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tubs%20come%20with%20a%20100-ml%20beaker%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20water%20is%20added%2C%20and%20a%20spoon%20is%20provided%20for%20easy%20eating.%20As%20Shalu%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20it%20as%20simple%20as%20possible%20for%20people%20to%20have%20a%20healthy%20meal%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20Whether%20you%20are%20at%20home%2C%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20or%20in%20a%20remote%20location%2C%20you%20can%20have%20a%20home-cooked%20meal%20ready%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%2C%20whose%20husband%20once%20struggled%20with%20finding%20vegetarian%20food%20while%20travelling%2C%20found%20the%20perfect%20solution.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20part%20about%20the%20brand%20is%20their%20tubs%2C%20as%20they%20are%20convenient%20and%20light%20enough%20to%20be%20carried%20across%20the%20globe.%20The%20food%20always%20tastes%20homemade%2C%20and%20each%20time%20we%20have%20purchased%20it%2C%20it%20has%20been%20consistently%20delicious.%20My%20husband%20now%20always%20carries%20a%20few%20tubs%20with%20him%2C%20and%20whenever%20he%20feels%20hungry%2C%20he%20simply%20adds%20hot%20water.%20Within%20just%20seven%20minutes%2C%20his%20meal%20is%20ready%2C%20and%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20him%20going%20without%20a%20proper%20meal%20when%20he%20is%20travelling.%20The%20peace%20of%20mind%20I%20have